<h1 align="center"style="color:blue">COLLEGE OF ENGINEERING CHENGANNUR</h1>
<marquee style ="color:green;font-size:20px">VISION:To emerge as an institution of excellence that imparts knowledge through education,learning,and research for the inclusive development of society.<br>

MISSION:To imparts engineering education that enables the students to design,develop and maintain systems,products and process for the society utilizing the evolving technology.
</marquee>
<h2 style ="color:white;background-color:red;">ABOUT US</h2>
<center>
<img src="cec.jpeg">
</center>
<p align ="justify">The college of Engineering Chengannur (CEC), was established by the Government of Kerala under the aegis of the IHRD,in the year 1993.It has been approved by AICTE and affiliated toAPJ Abdul Kalam Technological University(KTU).Ever since its inception,the college has maintained its eminence district the college has got access to all means of transport,communication and loading facilities.</p>
